metadata.name: The House
metadata.description:
We chose the easternmost island of the Ladoga skerries, named Ristisaari, for a reason. It has everything you need for a great trip: extraordinary color sky and water, rocks and huge boulders around, colorful moss, lingonberry-blackberry carpets and a view of the vast Ladoga Lake.
Here is the majesty and beauty of nature in Karelia.
We pitched our tent with a view of the sunset...

Camera: Pentax Spotmatic II
Lens: SMC Takumar 28mm F3.5
35mm film: Ðšodak Gold 200
Date: July 2022
